data.description: Welcome home to this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath home, move-In-ready home in maintenance free Waterview community!  The roof is approximately 1 year old!  The large living/dining room combo has vaulted ceilings and sliding glass doors to the large back lanai that has been converted to a large 27x10 Florida room with backyard access  w/concrete back fence wall.  The kitchen features plenty of cabinet space, stainless steel appliances, a pantry for extra storage, and a breakfast bar that opens to the dining and family room. The master bedroom has a walk-in closet and an ensuite master bathroom with a tiled shower. The guest bathroom is fully renovated with new fixtures, tub, and toilet. The home was recently replumbed. The Waterview community offers a community pool, tennis/pickleball/basketball court, fishing dock, clubhouse, and lawn maintenance.  Located in a highly desired area of south Lakeland and centrally located, with easy access to the Polk Parkway, close proximity to schools, shopping, and more!
